      "raw_text": "WAIST UNA VALLEY\n\n\nThe only way to become indie\ndependent is to work for your\nself. There is no more pleasant\nor profitable work than fruit\nraising, and in Washtucna val\nley nature has provided all the\nconditions necessary to success\nfull apple growing. A five or 10\nacre tract in Washtucna valley\nwill, If properly cared for, give\nyou comfortable home and\nfine income. 1t is in the center\nof great development and now\nis the time to get started. Prices\nare Etill low and terms easy.\nJoin Us on one of our excursions\nand look this valley over. 1t\nwill pay you to do so. Call. or\nwrite for booklet.\n\n\nTHE PALOUSE IRRIGATION\n\n\n& POWLR co.\n\n\n702 First Ave."
    }
